                                <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>Hormb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
<expan>gescheh<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ist, dabey <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Volkm<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> ratgesell,
                                <expan>gewese<ex>n</ex></expan> ist. Darumb
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>denselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Volkm<ex>er</ex></expan> verhört und ob wir des fürbas iht red
                                <expan>hört<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, <expan>darynne<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wolt<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir ew <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>antwurt<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, so wir peste
                                <expan>möcht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Wan wo wir
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb und
